      <title>中东紧张局势推动布伦特原油突破 90 美元，油价延续涨势</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-04/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-april-5</link>
      <description><![CDATA[继前一交易日突破每桶 90 美元关口后，由于中东紧张局势升级，油价连续第四天上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-04/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-april-5</guid>
